------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 44001.2
+++ ADMIRAL HANSON

+++ RED ALERT +++ RED ALERT +++ RED ALERT +++

A Borg invasion fleet has made it's way to the Alpha Quadrant.

Their target: Earth's solar system.

Every Starfleet ship has order to lay in course to system Wolf-359 in
order to intercept the Borg before they reach our Federation outposts.

Good luck, Captain!
