@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Hard
Solvable with unregistered version: Yes (tested)

This Borg scenario is not that hard as the one provided with
-Star_Trek-, but indeed: you have to make it against the Borg! You
have some more starbases this time, giving you a fair chance to get
a good ship and the other Federation ships are a bit stronger too,
which could give you the time you need. But don't forget: We are
talking about the Borg! Don't get assimilated!
_____________________________________________________________________

ENEMY UNITS

10x Borg Cube                                 2200
_____________________________________________________________________

YOUR UNITS

9x Starbase
USS CAIRO (NCC-42136, EXCELSIOR CLASS)         400
USS GORKON (NCC-50446, EXCELSIOR CLASS)        350
USS CONSTITUTION (NCC-1707-E, SOVEREIGN CLASS) 525
USS DEFIANT (NX-74205, DEFIANT CLASS)          450
USS BOZEMAN (NCC-1941, SOYUZ CLASS)            280
